### Morning Flow
1. User receives notification
2. Inputs energy/mood/sleep
3. App shows prioritized tasks (Eisenhower-style UI)
4. User confirms plan

### Evening Flow
1. User receives notification
2. Inputs completed/added tasks
3. Optional: short question (mood/feedback)

### Weekly Flow
1. On Selected Day, user gets summary of previous week
2. AI-generated insight card appears